body.visual-sandbox #sandbox-host {
  overflow: auto;
}
div.root {
  height: 100%;
  display: flex;
  flex-flow: column;
}
nav {
  background: #f8f9fa;
}
nav.navbar {
  flex: 0 1 auto;
}
div.ag-grid {
  flex: 1 1 auto;
}
.alert-shown {
  opacity: 1;
  transition: all 250ms linear;
}
.alert-hidden {
  opacity: 0;
  transition: all 250ms linear 1s;
}
.btn:disabled {
  opacity: 0.25;
}
.Mui-disabled {
  color: #a8c30b;
  opacity: 0.25;
}
.MuiSvgIcon-root {
  color: #a8c30b;
}
.MuiCircularProgress-svg {
  color: #a8c30b;
}
.btn:size {
  padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
}
ol,
ul {
  padding-left: 0;
}
table th.group {
  position: sticky;
  left: 0;
  z-index: 2;
}
table td.group {
  position: sticky;
  left: 0;
  z-index: 2;
}
#modellingMessage {
  align-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
}
#faTableCells {
  height: 5rem;
  padding-bottom: 1.5rem;
}
.fontawesome-icons-buttons {
  height: 1em;
  color: #a8c30b;
  vertical-align: -0.125em;
}
.fontawesome-indicator-failure {
  height: 1em;
  color: #e0200b;
  vertical-align: -0.125em;
}
.fontawesome-indicator-success {
  height: 1em;
  color: #a8c30b;
  vertical-align: -0.125em;
}
.unsavedIcon {
  position: fixed;
  z-index: 1;
}
.input {
  position: relative;
  border-width: 0px;
  z-index: 0;
}
.input:focus {
  border-width: 0px;
  outline-color: black;
}
.input:read-only {
  border-width: 0px;
  outline-color: #727272;
  cursor: default;
}
